---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Github, Mail } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<Layout>
  <article class="prose prose-invert xs:py-20 mx-auto max-w-2xl space-y-6 px-6">
    <h1 class="xs:text-4xl font-bold sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">About Me</h1>
    <p>I'm Slade, a self-taught full-stack developer based in South Africa.</p>
    <p>
      I started learning to code in mid-2025 with no prior experience — just
      curiosity and a lot of time in the terminal. In under a year I went from
      zero to building full-stack applications with custom authentication, REST
      APIs, and real databases. Not because I followed a curriculum, but because
      I kept asking "how does this actually work?" and refused to stop until I
      had an answer.
    </p>
    <p>
      That curiosity is how I work. I don't copy-paste solutions. I dig in,
      figure out the fundamentals, and build things properly.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of web development I'm deep into Linux — I daily drive Arch (btw)
      with a custom Hyprland setup — and I'm learning ethical hacking and
      security in my spare time. I'm drawn to understanding how systems work at
      a lower level, which makes me a better developer at every level above it.
    </p>
    <p>
      What I build tends to be practical. A CRM for a real estate business. A
      local UI for testing language models. A restaurant site with smooth
      transitions and a real reservations flow. I'm not interested in
      impressive-looking demos that don't do anything — I care about software
      that actually works for the people using it.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're a business that needs something built, or a team looking for
      someone who learns fast and takes the work seriously — I'd love to talk.
    </p>
    <div class="not-prose flex items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/thecentinol"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-(--accent)"
      >
        <Github size={20} />
        Github
      </a>

      <a
        href="mailto:centinol@proton.me"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-(--accent)"
      >
        <Mail size={20} />
        Email
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
